div.div:
Application
Programming Interfaces are methods of communication between information
systems. By making sure that systems are interconnected and
interoperable, you can avoid the setbacks in development process when
some external API function wouldn't be accessible the way it was
designed in high-level concept diagram.

div.div:
Set your design goals (hills), Involve users early, create a
design that will deliver value (utilize playbacks).Wireframe,
is a visualisation tool for presenting proposed functions, structure
and content of a App. A wireframe separates the graphic elements of a
App from the functional elements in such a way that Mobile teams can
easily explain how users will interact with the App. IBM Design - Visual Layout
Storyboard, A storyboard is a graphic organization that provides the
viewer with a high-level view of a project.
IBM Design - Interaction
